  m_text: "\"I approached charcoal as a way to express my artistic sensibilities.
    It symbolized the cyclical nature of life and death\u2026 As wood transforms
    into charcoal through the fiery furnace of a kiln, it retains its inherent integrity.\"\n\n\u2014
    Lee Bae (\u674E\u57F9)"
