  m_text: "\"The work Landscape expresses a territory or the surface of continents
    by fixing charcoal on top of a flat surface. I wanted to create a space where
    charcoal, the chaos created by fire, and human sensibility could meet.\"\n\n\u2014
    Lee Bae (\u674E\u57F9)"
