  m_text: "\"From early on, I was drawn to the evocative power of a specific medium
    and wanted to focus on its essence and place it at the center of my work. I never
    felt the need to use the figurative language which I think can be restrictive.\"\n\n\u2014
    Lee Bae (\u674E\u57F9)"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
